class.name: Window
class.abstract: Represents the window.

method.name: Activate
method.abstract: Activates a window.

method.name: ActivateNext
method.abstract: Activates the window following the current active one in the window collection.

method.name: ActivatePrevious
method.abstract: Activates the window preceding the current active one in the window collection.

method.name: Close
method.abstract: Closes the window.

method.name: NewWindow
method.abstract: Creates a new window.

method.name: PrintOut
method.abstract: Prints the active viewer of the window according to the window's page setup on the default printer.

method.name: PrintToFile
method.abstract: Prints the active viewer of the window according to the window's page setup in a file instead of being sent to a printer.

method.name: ActiveViewer
method.abstract: Returns the active viewer in the window.

method.name: Caption
method.abstract: Returns or sets the window caption.

method.name: Height
method.abstract: Returns or sets the window height.

method.name: Left
method.abstract: Returns or sets the distance of the window with respect to the inner left side of the frame.

method.name: PageSetup
method.abstract: Returns or sets the page setup of the window.

method.name: Top
method.abstract: Returns or sets the distance of the window with respect to the inner top side of the frame.

method.name: Viewers
method.abstract: Returns the collection of viewers attached to the window.

method.name: Width
method.abstract: Returns or sets the window width.

method.name: WindowState
method.abstract: Returns or sets the window state.

class.name: Windows
class.abstract: A collection of all the Window objects currently managed by the application.

method.name: Arrange
method.abstract: Arranges all the windows of the collection.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a window using its index or its name from the Windows collection.
